OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774461963
OL,3,CAmbulance service cuts response times
OL,4,Cbut falls short of national target
OL,6,FSouth Western Ambulance Service has
OL,7,Fcut its average response time for
OL,8,Furgent treatment and is reaching
OL,9,Fpatients faster, but is still failing
OL,10,Fto meet national targets.
OL,12,FNew figures from NHS England South
OL,13,FWest show ambulances reached category
OL,14,Ftwo patients 38 minutes faster this
OL,15,Fwinter, with average response times
OL,16,Fdown from 72 minutes in 2023 to 34
OL,17,Fminutes in 2026.
OL,19,FCategory two calls include serious
OL,20,Femergencies such as strokes,
OL,21,Fdifficulty breathing and chest pains.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
