OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774461963
OL,3,CAmbulance service cuts response times
OL,4,Cbut falls short of national target
OL,6,FHowever, the improved response time
OL,7,Ffalls short of the national target of
OL,8,F30 minutes, which was relaxed from the
OL,9,Fpre-pandemic target of 18 minutes in
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FDr Trevor Smith, South West Medical
OL,13,FDirector, said the figures are
OL,14,Fpromising but "there is still far more
OL,15,Fto do."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774461963
OL,3,CAmbulance service cuts response times
OL,4,Cbut falls short of national target
OL,6,F"Because the South West is so rural
OL,7,Fand coastal, and has such an older
OL,8,Fpopulation, it provides additional
OL,9,Fchallenges to getting to people in a
OL,10,Ftimely way and also in the levels of
OL,11,Fdemand for care that we see," he said.
OL,13,F"But every minute counts in an
OL,14,Femergency, and I'm incredibly grateful
OL,15,Fto the thousands of paramedics,
OL,16,Fnurses, doctors and other staff who've
OL,17,Fmade this improvement.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774461963
OL,3,CAmbulance service cuts response times
OL,4,Cbut falls short of national target
OL,6,F"The NHS is starting to turn a corner
OL,7,Fbut there is still far more to do and
OL,8,Fwe are determined to eliminate delays
OL,9,Faltogether, including a zero tolerance
OL,10,Fapproach to corridor care."
OL,12,FThe figures also show that the average
OL,13,Fambulance handover time fell from 73
OL,14,Fminutes in 2023 to 34 minutes in 2026.
OL,15,FThe national target is for a patient
OL,16,Fto be admitted to hospital within 15
OL,17,Fminutes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774461963
OL,3,CAmbulance service cuts response times
OL,4,Cbut falls short of national target
OL,6,FNHS England South West said the
OL,7,Fimproved response and handover times
OL,8,Fcome despite the ambulance service
OL,9,Freporting a 22% increase in demand.
OL,11,FSouth Western Ambulance Service Chief
OL,12,FExecutive, Dr John Martin, said:
OL,13,F"Demand for our services remains high,
OL,14,Fand we are steadfast in our commitment
OL,15,Fto ensuring every patient receives the
OL,16,Fmost appropriate and timely care
OL,17,Fpossible.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774461963
OL,3,CAmbulance service cuts response times
OL,4,Cbut falls short of national target
OL,6,F"We continue to strengthen our remote
OL,7,Fclinical support within our Emergency
OL,8,FOperations Centres, by assessing 999
OL,9,Fcalls to determine the best response
OL,10,Ffor patients.
OL,12,F"This ensures patients receive the
OL,13,Fmost appropriate care for them, and it
OL,14,Falso helps keep our ambulances
OL,15,Favailable for those in urgent and life-
OL,16,Fthreatening situations.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1774461963
OL,3,CAmbulance service cuts response times
OL,4,Cbut falls short of national target
OL,6,F"Improvements to ambulance handovers
OL,7,Fhave gone hand in hand with efforts
OL,8,Ffrom our crews to reduce clinically
OL,9,Favoidable conveyances to Emergency
OL,10,FDepartments, through optimising
OL,11,Fcommunity services and arranging care
OL,12,Fpackages for patients closer to home,
OL,13,Fespecially for frail and older
OL,14,Fpatients wherever possible."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@\O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
